---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Editorial and Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="Read PeptideRundown's editorial independence, advertising, sponsorship, and affiliate disclosure policy."
>
  <section class="bg-surface py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary mb-3">Disclosure</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-text mb-6">Editorial independence and monetization policy.</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p>PeptideRundown is built around independent educational content. We do not sell peptides or provide medical services.</p>
        <h2>Advertising and Sponsorships</h2>
        <p>We may eventually accept advertising, sponsorships, or affiliate relationships. If that happens, sponsored or affiliate content will be labeled clearly, and commercial relationships will not determine medical or scientific conclusions.</p>
        <h2>No Vendor Endorsement</h2>
        <p>Mentions of companies, products, clinics, pharmacies, or research vendors are for informational context only unless explicitly labeled otherwise.</p>
        <h2>Corrections</h2>
        <p>If you believe a page is inaccurate, contact <a href="mailto:hello@peptiderundown.com">hello@peptiderundown.com</a> with the page URL and supporting source material.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
